      Adding a Relay Application (cont'd)
      ===================================
      If the application does not exist, the Add a Record screen
      will be displayed, requiring the configuration to be input.
      The program will display the valid data ranges for each field, and
      if an invalid value is input, an error message will be displayed,
      and you will be required to input the parameter again. NOTE: if
      you enter "E" while adding, the menu will be displayed and the ADD
      will not be performed!
 
      Modifying a Relay Application
      =============================
      To modify an application, enter "2" (for Modify Application),
      and press return.  The program will then prompt for the application
      number. If the record does not exist, an error message will be
      displayed, and you will be prompted for another application.
      If the configuration exists, the Modify a Application configuration
 
 
