      Deleting an Application
      =======================
      This option will allow a relay application configuration to be deleted.
      To delete an application, enter "3" and press return.  Enter the
      application number, and if it exists, the Delete an Application
      screen will be displayed. If the record does not exist, an error message
      will be displayed, and you must re-enter the number.  Once the Delete
      Screen has been displayed, look at the configuration information to
      ensure that this is the correct record.  If you wish to delete
      it, enter "Y" and press return, and a message will be displayed
      informing that the record was deleted.  If you no not wish to
      delete the record, enter "N" and the station will not be deleted.
 
 
 
 
 
 
